infiltrate (p = 0.001), low fibrosis (p = 0.007), lower p53 expression (p = 
0.03) and positive estrogen receptor (p = 0.03); other factors were marginally 
associated: positive progesterone receptor (p = 0.07) and having less than 6 
positive lymph nodes (p = 0.07).

